                Mr. Kenneth Lindsay (Kilmarnock)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-a9aebd88-a1ba-4865-ad33-b9eda793a39c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
