<p class="">I did not say the statement was not correct. I say that the evidence in the court was not in accordance with the actual facts with what <span id="986" class="column-number" data-column-number="986"></span> happened in the pit. If this lad had had a lawyer—</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
