<p class="">How long has the Minister enjoyed that priority?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f91c33ed-c7aa-4761-ad93-cfb73b7e2f10" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
