        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">With regard to this machinery in America, is the Minister able to get any idea of the diggers, scrapers and other <span id="1007" class="column-number" data-column-number="1007"></span> necessary machinery which is lying idle in British building yards in this country and which could be utilised?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-b8b1dc4b-1eb7-444f-9caa-d6da8d9e16e4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
